      "content": "Look, you're talking about a 6-hour window of total downtime. That's millions in losses and a massive headache with the board. Are you absolutely sure this is an \"immediate\" must-do? If it's just a theoretical risk or if it's behind enough layers of existing security, can we not just monitor it and patch it during the scheduled window next weekend instead? I need to know if you're being overly cautious here.",
